    "example": "Ambush (ALPHA-1 · E03, uncommon, TRAP, cost 2)",
    "note": "Only event-specific values. Shares with unit/location cards: palette, fonts, gold cost coin, glass panels (#060c18 @78%, 1px #1a2540, r10, backdrop-blur 6px), full-bleed hatch ('\\' 45°, 2px/16px, #fff @5%), rarity footer. Measured from live DOM at 1:1.",
